.7735094548622523e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite a tough loss to Brazil and some heated exchanges on the court last Friday, Humana-Paredes experienced a heartwarming moment on a Parisian street corner after the match concluded in three sets.\", \"from\": 283, \"to\": 483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 307, \"end\": 313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7639063193724159, \"rank\": 0.3054850018432958, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 366, \"end\": 380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Humana-Paredes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a touching display of sportsmanship, Brazilian fans greeted the Canadian athlete with overwhelming support following her country's defeat in the Olympic final.\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 647, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 552, \"end\": 560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9653301650739051, \"rank\": 0.03589066230000276, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Humana-Paredes was surrounded by a crowd of fans who had come to celebrate their team's victory.\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 744, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 648, \"end\": 662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Humana-Paredes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clearly touched by the emotional moment, the 31-year-old Toronto native shared a video of the scene to her Instagram account with the following caption:  \\\"This is what I walked out to after losing the Olympic finals.\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 962, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 803, \"end\": 810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"score\": 0.9999974694553844, \"rank\": 2.250915255126972e-06, \"text\": \"Toronto\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\"}, {\"begin\": 853, \"end\": 862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.315945599829127e-17, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While looking for my boyfriend, a group of Brazilians started chanting my name and welcomed me with open arms.\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 1073, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1006, \"end\": 1016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5937982763874875, \"rank\": 0.684071973557881, \"text\": \"Brazilians\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They celebrated like I was a champion.\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1112, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These are the Brazilian fans I know and love.\\\"\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1159, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Melissa Humana-Paredes (@melissahumanaparedes)    Proudly donning her silver medal around her neck, Hamana-Paredes eventually found her boyfriend through the sea of fans chanting her name, which only fueled the electric atmosphere around her.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1190, \"end\": 1204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Humana-Paredes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Talk about a silver lining.\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, despite the loss, Humana-Paredes and Wilkerson made history by becoming the first Canadian beach volleyball team to play in a gold medal game at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1487, \"end\": 1501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Humana-Paredes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Humana-Paredes\"}, {\"begin\": 1551, \"end\": 1559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9653301650739051, \"rank\": 0.03589066230000276, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Melissa Humana-Paredes (@melissahumanaparedes)    Their silver medal not only added to Canada's tally, bringing the total to 27 medals in Paris, but also set the record for the country's largest hardware haul in a non-boycotted Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 163